      <title>为什么俄罗斯人参加奥运会，而俄罗斯人却不参加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/why-russia-belarus-aren-t-competing-at-paris-olympics-but-their-athletes-are</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯的传统体育实力使得其国歌成为现代奥运会颁奖仪式上的常规旋律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/why-russia-belarus-aren-t-competing-at-paris-olympics-but-their-athletes-are</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
