    <item>
      <title>联合国称恐怖分子正在寻找符合伊斯兰教法的加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/terrorists-are-finding-path-to-sharia-compliant-crypto-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据联合国的报告，伊斯兰国坚称其用于资助恐怖活动的加密货币必须符合伊斯兰教法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/terrorists-are-finding-path-to-sharia-compliant-crypto-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 15:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
